<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> M.TAlibi: Drois et economie en Ifrigiya. Tuniis, ١٩٩٢<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أمنية محمد رضا [م. طالبى M. Talbi]<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
